Notes: Sophomore center Paige Ballinger scores 17 points to lead three Wildcats in
double figures as WSC defeats UMD 68-52. Head Coach Chris Kielsmeier is now
tied for the all-time wins at WSC with Ryun Williams (1998-2008) with a record
of 182-52 in his tenure at Wayne State.
Game.Officials: Darin Berg,  Bryan Rump,  Terry Reynolds
